text: The Seibu Ikebukuro Line is a train line in Japan that goes from Ikebukuro to Seibu-Chichibu and back, stopping at many stations on the way. This is a list of abbreviations for the table: LO: LOCAL SE: Semi Express EX: Express LE: Lim.
